laser light striper has seen a

00:30:12.350 --> 00:30:15.400
can on top of the desk
in front of it.

00:30:15.400 --> 00:30:20.060
When this happens the robots
and deploys its arm.

00:30:20.060 --> 00:30:21.560
You can see the arm
going out now.

